>   VS Raiding, New spawn rates, my thoughts</span><hr size=1> They just upped the spawn rate on VS. That should help shorten the list a bit or at least speed it along. Here is my 2 cents: after VS pops you should have 24 hours to organize and kill him, maybe combined with increased spawn times more folks will get a shot at him. I dont think 24 hours (or maybe less)is too much to ask considering most folks' level now.<br>
<br>
Just my opinion, I could be wrong. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umaarkus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maarkus</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 50<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/17/01 10:21:29 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: VS Raiding, New spawn rates, my thoughts</span><hr size=1> Hmm from my understanding of the patch message rangers and druids can spawn him at any time they needed to do the quest<br>
<br>
<br>
&gt;We have increased the spawn rate of Venril Sathir and his &gt;skeletal remains. Please note that only Rangers and Druids &gt;will be able to trigger the spawn for the skeletal &gt;remains, and those remains will only be dropping items for &gt;those epic quests. Hopefully these changes will &gt;dramatically reduce the competition and resentment over &gt;this spawn.<br>
<br>
I might be misinterpretting the quest as being when VS isntup the remains are.. /shrug<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uzythen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zythen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 150<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/17/01 10:29:00 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.nettally.com/xerec/wolf2.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: VS Raiding, New spawn rates, my thoughts</span><hr size=1> I hope that is the case since the remains were only a one time deal each time VS was dropped in the recent past.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uzestrenocya.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zestrenocya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Norrath's Finest Taxi Service</span><br>  Posts: 1159<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/17/01 1:01:58 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: VS Raiding, New spawn rates, my thoughts</span><hr size=1> I imagine its just the remains, and not VS proper, who will spawn more often. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utatterdmalion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tatter DMalion</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 90<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/17/01 1:28:48 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: VS Raiding, New spawn rates, my thoughts</span><hr size=1> My take on it is that VS now will spawn more than once a week.  Unless, the person typing the patch message has poor grammer.<br>
<br>
I'm curious to how fast the remains will repop for epic parts.  Poor wizards are apparently having to still rely on the regular VS for the staff. (My appologies if VS does not drop an epic staff for Wizards.  I'm only a bard.)<br>
<br>
I have my doubts if this will really help the list or not.  Remains will be like Ragefire I imagine.  So this list won't really shrink, maybe move a little faster.<br>
<br>
Tatter D'Malion <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unicophorus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nicophorus</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://homepages.go.com/~aela_eq/Shield.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Less Talk, More Fight</span><br>  Posts: 636<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/17/01 1:30:20 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   A question?</span><hr size=1> How much of the VS backlog is Ranger/Druid epic and how much is folks trying to drop him for other reasons?<br>
<br>
I suppose there's no real direction to go with this until the exact meaning of the patch message has been played out in game once or twice... just curious as a bystander on this one...<br>
